      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "snippet": "North Vancouver offers several Registered Clinical Counsellors (RCCs) specializing in couples therapy, focusing on communication, conflict resolution, and rebuilding connection. Key providers include The Relationship Clinic, Bach Counselling Group, Lynn Valley Counselling, and Urban Balance Wellness, offering both in-person and virtual sessions for various relationship structures."
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "snippet": "Top North Vancouver Couples Therapy Options (RCCs)"
      },
      {
        "type": "list",
        "list": [
          {
            "snippet": "The Relationship Clinic: Specializes in relationship issues including communication, intimacy, and infidelity, often utilizing evidence-based, neuroscience-informed approaches.",
            "snippet_links": [
              {
                "text": "The Relationship Clinic",
                "link": "https://relationshipclinic.ca/"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "snippet": "Bach Counselling Group: Led by Heather Bach, this group offers in-office and virtual couples counseling focusing on repairing relationships and improving communication tools.",
            "snippet_links": [
              {
                "text": "Bach Counselling Group",
                "link": "https://www.bachcounselling.com/"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "snippet": "Urban Balance Wellness: Provides inclusive, trauma-informed relationship counseling for couples, including traditional, open, and polyamorous relationships.",
            "snippet_links": [
              {
                "text": "Urban Balance Wellness",
                "link": "https://urbanbalance.ca/"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "snippet": "Lynn Valley Counselling: Offers tailored counseling for couples dealing with life transitions, communication issues, and conflict.",
            "snippet_links": [
              {
                "text": "Lynn Valley Counselling",
                "link": "https://lynnvalleycounselling.com/"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "snippet": "Illuminate Counselling: Features RCCs specializing in premarital counseling and relationship strengthening through video or in-person sessions.",
            "snippet_links": [
              {
                "text": "Illuminate Counselling",
                "link": "https://illuminate-online.com/"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "snippet": "Helen Whitehead R.C.C.: Focuses on attachment injuries, communication strategies, and building healthy relationship dynamics.",
            "snippet_links": [
              {
                "text": "Helen Whitehead R.C.C.",
                "link": "https://www.helenwhitehead.ca/"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "snippet": "Key Areas of Focus"
      },
      {
        "type": "list",
        "list": [
          {
            "snippet": "Communication & Conflict: Resolving gridlock and improving interaction patterns."
          },
          {
            "snippet": "Reconnection: Rebuilding intimacy and reducing emotional disconnection."
          },
          {
            "snippet": "Specialized Needs: Dealing with betrayal, infidelity, or differing parenting styles."
          },
          {
            "snippet": "Alternative Structures: Providing support for LGBTQ2S+, polyamorous, and non-monogamous relationships."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
